{"tid":1810031,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Google 廣東話輸入法有bug，係咁食我字，點算，懷疑關chrome 事，但我搵唔到答案","createTime":"2020-01-03T13:42:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T03:25:00.000Z","uid":57369,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"71ae0999148ecb90025cedb0ff6441ffc87c493e","tid":1810031,"uid":57369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T13:42:41.000Z","msg":"舉個例子，而家我想打「小明上廣州見特朗普」<br />\n<br />\n而家我打咗 <code>小明上北京見特朗普</code><br />\n咁我就打錯字啦，然後我就響 <code>上</code> 字同個 <code>北</code> 字中間打返 <code>廣州</code><br />\n<br />\n但係最後打完竟然會自動delete 咗 <code>廣州見特朗普</code> 呢六隻字<br />\n<br />\n唔係個個網站上面輸入都會出現呢個問題，但係數量都不少<br />\n有無人有解決方法？因為真係好滋擾<br />\n<br />\nPS：已經排除咗係我其他嘅extension做出嚟<br />\nPSS：Google 過冇答案"},{"pid":"134f85ec20337fee0af7bd3fef7f8b482f3e90cc","tid":1810031,"uid":46808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T13:45:24.000Z","msg":"用咗幾年 無呢個問題 觀察多幾日先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46706cabf1c2297e16880d5cf01b3065f52eb822","tid":1810031,"uid":11598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T13:47:27.000Z","msg":"好多網站都有問題<br />\n例如facebook打完字噤backspace會成行清晒<br />\n唯有開第個tab打完再paste上去"},{"pid":"955d83565e7c5b4b57d967b514156cb9a3768741","tid":1810031,"uid":57369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"134f85ec20337fee0af7bd3fef7f8b482f3e90cc","tid":1810031,"uid":46808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T13:45:24.000Z","msg":"用咗幾年 無呢個問題 觀察多幾日先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T13:52:43.000Z","msg":"係Google Chrome extension 嗰個版本先會有呢個問題<br />\nAndroid 版正常運作"},{"pid":"5a949650b2e4b200e0e32c33dc26bacd083925ed","tid":1810031,"uid":57369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46706cabf1c2297e16880d5cf01b3065f52eb822","tid":1810031,"uid":11598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T13:47:27.000Z","msg":"好多網站都有問題<br />\n例如f